    <div id='timeline'>
      <h2>A Brief Timeline of Leonardo DaVinci's Life</h2>
      <ul>
        <li> <strong>April 15th, 1452: </strong>Leonardo is born in the Tuscan town of Vinci.</li>
        <li><strong>1466: </strong>Leonardo begins his apprenticeship with Verrochio.</li>
        <li><strong>1487: </strong>Leonardo sketches the Vitruvian Man.</li>
        <li><strong>1495-1498: </strong>Leonardo paints the Last Supper.</li>
        <li><strong>1503-1506: </strong>Leonardo paints the Mona Lisa.</li>
        <li><strong>1513-1516: </strong>Leonardo paints Saint John the Baptist.</li>
        <li><strong>May 2nd, 1519: </strong> Leonardo passes away in France.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <div id='notable-works-text'> 
